"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${refdes:PIN_BASE_NAME(pin)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Basis pin-navn (ignorerer alternativer)</samp></"
"td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${U1:PIN_BASE_NAME(5)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>PA9</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${refdes:PIN_ALT_LIST(pin)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Alle alternative pin-funktioner (ekskluderer "
"basisnavn)</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${U1:PIN_ALT_LIST(5)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>USART1_TX, TIM1_CH2, I2C1_SCL</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${refdes:SHORT_NET_NAME(pin)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Kort netnavn eller NC hvis uforbundet</samp></"
"td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${J1:SHORT_NET_NAME(3)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>GND</samp> eller <samp>NC</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${refdes:NET_CLASS(pin)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>NetClass for pin</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${J1:NET_CLASS(1)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Power</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <th>Escape-sekvenser</th>\n"
"        <th></th>\n"
"        <th></th>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>\\${LITERAL}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${LITERAL}</samp> (ikke udvidet)</td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Price: \\$25.00</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Price: $25.00</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>\\@{x+y}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>@{x+y}</samp> (ikke evalueret)</td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <th>Indlejrede variabler</th>\n"
"        <th></th>\n"
"        <th></th>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${J1:REFERENCE(@{${ROW}+2})}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>J1B</samp> (når ROW=0, pin 2 i enhed B)</td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${J1:NET_NAME(${COL})}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Dynamisk netopslag i tabeller</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <th>Tabelcelle-referencer</th>\n"
"        <th></th>\n"
"        <th></th>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${CELL(\"A0\")}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Evalueret værdi fra celle A0</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${CELL(0, 1)}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Værdi fra række 0, kolonne 1</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${CELL(${ADDR})}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Dynamisk cellereference</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>${CELL(${ROW}-1, ${COL})}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>Værdi fra cellen ovenover (hvis ROW > 0)</samp></"
"td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <th>Bus-definition</th>\n"
"        <th>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</th>\n"
"        <th>Resulterende net</th>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>prefix[m..n]</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>prefixm til prefixn</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>D[0..7]</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>D0, D1, D2, D3, D4, D5, D6, D7</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>{net1 net2 ...}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>net1, net2, ...</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>{SCL SDA}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>SCL, SDA</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>prefix{net1 net2 ...}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>prefix.net1, prefix.net2, ...</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>USB1{D+ D-}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>USB1.D+, USB1.D-</samp></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>MEM{D[1..2] LATCH}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br> <samp>MEM.D1, MEM.D2, MEM.LATCH</samp> </td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td>&nbsp;<br><samp>MEM{D_{[1..2]} ~{LATCH}}</samp></td>\n"
"        <td></td>\n"
"        <td> <samp>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<sub>&nbsp;</sub>&nbsp; "
"&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<sub>&nbsp;</sub>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"&nbsp;<u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u></samp><br> <samp>MEM.D<sub>1</"
"sub>, MEM.D<sub>2</sub>, MEM.LATCH</samp> </td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"    <tr>\n"
"        <td><br></td>\n"
"    </tr>\n"
"</table>\n"
"<p></p>\n"
"<p></p>\n"
"<i>Bemærk at markup har forrang over bus-definitioner.</i>\n"
"<p></p>\n"
"<p><b>Pin-funktioner:</b> Finder automatisk den korrekte enhedsplacering. "
"For multi-enheds-symboler virker funktioner som <samp>NET_NAME(pin)</samp> "
"selv hvis pin'en er i en anden enhed end den på det aktuelle ark.</p>\n"
"<p><b>Tabelcelle-referencer:</b> Funktionen <samp>CELL()</samp> virker kun i "
"tabelceller. Brug <samp>${CELL(\"A0\")}</samp> eller <samp>${CELL(row, col)}"
"</samp> til at referere til andre celler i samme tabel. Række- og "
"kolonnenumre er 0-baserede (A0 er første række, første kolonne). CELL "
"returnerer den evaluerede/viste værdi, ikke den rå celletekst.</p>\n"
"<p><b>Indlejrede variabler:</b> Variabler kan indeholde andre variabler. "
"Indre variabler udfoldes først. Maksimal indlejringsdybde: 6 niveauer.</p>\n"
"<p><b>Fejlmeddelelser:</b></p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li><samp>&lt;UNRESOLVED: token&gt;</samp> - Variabel eller funktion kan "
"ikke løses</li>\n"
"<li><samp>&lt;Unit X not placed&gt;</samp> - Pin'en er i en enhed der ikke "
"er placeret på noget ark</li>\n"
"<li><samp>&lt;Unresolved: Cell X not found&gt;</samp> - Celleadressen er "
"uden for tabellens grænser</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"\n"

